reviewText: I really liked this movie. I had it when I was kid, but I think it got lost. So I saw it on amazon and had to buy it.
If you love classic cartoon from the eighties from your childhood then you will this cartoon for youself so get it!

I remember watching the show in the 80's and I am currently doing a project in my Develomental Psych class that involves a children's television show.  I have had this video since I was little and am using it as my material.  It is good fun entertainment and is enjoyable by all ages.  I highly recommend it to young ones.
